WITH UserBadges AS (
    SELECT 
        UserId, 
        COUNT(CASE WHEN Class = 1 THEN 1 END) AS GoldBadges,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN Class = 2 THEN 1 END) AS SilverBadges,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN Class = 3 THEN 1 END) AS BronzeBadges
    FROM Badges
    GROUP BY UserId
),
PostStatistics AS (
    SELECT 
        p.OwnerUserId,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN p.PostTypeId = 1 THEN 1 END) AS QuestionCount,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN p.PostTypeId = 2 THEN 1 END) AS AnswerCount,
        SUM(p.Score) AS TotalScore,
        SUM(p.ViewCount) AS TotalViews
    FROM Posts p
    LEFT JOIN Users u ON p.OwnerUserId = u.Id
    WHERE u.Reputation > 1000
    GROUP BY p.OwnerUserId
),
RecentActivity AS (
    SELECT 
        p.OwnerUserId,
        MAX(p.LastActivityDate) AS LastActivityDate
    FROM Posts p
    GROUP BY p.OwnerUserId
)
SELECT 
    u.DisplayName,
    COALESCE(ub.GoldBadges, 0) AS GoldBadges,
    COALESCE(ub.SilverBadges, 0) AS SilverBadges,
    COALESCE(ub.BronzeBadges, 0) AS BronzeBadges,
    ps.QuestionCount, 
    ps.AnswerCount,
    ps.TotalScore,
    ps.TotalViews,
    ra.LastActivityDate
FROM Users u
LEFT JOIN UserBadges ub ON u.Id = ub.UserId
LEFT JOIN PostStatistics ps ON u.Id = ps.OwnerUserId
LEFT JOIN RecentActivity ra ON u.Id = ra.OwnerUserId
WHERE (ps.QuestionCount > 5 OR ps.AnswerCount > 10)
AND ra.LastActivityDate > CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '6' MONTHS
ORDER BY ps.TotalScore DESC, u.DisplayName ASC

SELECT COALESCE("t10"."DISPLAYNAME", "t10"."DISPLAYNAME") AS "DISPLAYNAME", "t10"."GOLDBADGES", "t10"."SILVERBADGES", "t10"."BRONZEBADGES", "t10"."QUESTIONCOUNT", "t10"."ANSWERCOUNT", "t10"."TOTALSCORE", "t10"."TOTALVIEWS", "t10"."LASTACTIVITYDATE"
FROM (SELECT "t8"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", CASE WHEN "t8"."GOLDBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t8"."GOLDBADGES" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "GOLDBADGES", CASE WHEN "t8"."SILVERBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t8"."SILVERBADGES" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "SILVERBADGES", CASE WHEN "t8"."BRONZEBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t8"."BRONZEBADGES" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "BRONZEBADGES", "t8"."QUESTIONCOUNT", "t8"."ANSWERCOUNT", "t8"."TOTALSCORE", "t8"."TOTALVIEWS", CAST("t2"."LASTACTIVITYDATE" AS TIMESTAMP) AS "LASTACTIVITYDATE"
FROM (SELECT "OwnerUserId", MAX("LastActivityDate") AS "LASTACTIVITYDATE"
FROM "Posts"
GROUP BY "OwnerUserId"
HAVING MAX("LastActivityDate") > CAST((CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '6' MONTH) AS TIMESTAMP)) AS "t2"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "Users0"."Id", "Users0"."Reputation", "Users0"."CreationDate", "Users0"."DisplayName", "Users0"."LastAccessDate", "Users0"."WebsiteUrl", "Users0"."Location", "Users0"."AboutMe", "Users0"."Views", "Users0"."UpVotes", "Users0"."DownVotes", "Users0"."ProfileImageUrl", "Users0"."AccountId", "t7"."USERID", "t7"."GOLDBADGES", "t7"."SILVERBADGES", "t7"."BRONZEBADGES", CAST("t6"."OWNERUSERID" AS INTEGER) AS "OWNERUSERID", CAST("t6"."QUESTIONCOUNT" AS BIGINT) AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", CAST("t6"."ANSWERCOUNT" AS BIGINT) AS "ANSWERCOUNT", CAST("t6"."TOTALSCORE" AS INTEGER) AS "TOTALSCORE", CAST("t6"."TOTALVIEWS" AS INTEGER) AS "TOTALVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT "Posts0"."OwnerUserId" AS "OWNERUSERID", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("Posts0"."PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("Posts0"."PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "ANSWERCOUNT", SUM("Posts0"."Score") AS "TOTALSCORE", SUM("Posts0"."ViewCount") AS "TOTALVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM "Users"
WHERE "Reputation" > 1000) AS "t3"
INNER JOIN "Posts" AS "Posts0" ON "t3"."Id" = "Posts0"."OwnerUserId"
GROUP BY "Posts0"."OwnerUserId"
HAVING COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("Posts0"."PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) > 5 OR COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("Posts0"."PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) > 10) AS "t6"
INNER JOIN ("Users" AS "Users0" LEFT JOIN (SELECT "USERID", COUNT("FD_COL_1") AS "GOLDBADGES", COUNT("FD_COL_2") AS "SILVERBADGES", COUNT("FD_COL_3") AS "BRONZEBADGES"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "USERID") AS "t7" ON "Users0"."Id" = "t7"."USERID") ON "t6"."OWNERUSERID" = "Users0"."Id") AS "t8" ON "t2"."OwnerUserId" = "t8"."Id"
ORDER BY "t8"."TOTALSCORE" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t8"."DisplayName") AS "t10"
